CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 8, 1945, pg. 4, reads: "Sixty-five Years of Progress - Warren Methodist Church is holding its sixty-fifth anniversary celebration.  The present edifice is one of the finest in Pittsburgh.  The Rev. J. O. Williams is pastor."
